      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HE'S MAGIC (1) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fourth (29.61) at Sandown latest. Form here sound including three wins. Yet to miss the placings in nine runs from this box, including seven wins. Rates on top in this line up. HIGHLY POTENT (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (29.82) last time in a Special conditions G3 at Sandown. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. One of the main contenders. PAW DAMON (2) has a strong record this journey with two wins and a minor from five starts. Placed last time (29.94) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 0.7 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. PRISON BREAK (7) was in the money last start and poses a threat again.",
